{"word":"παρακλιδόν","slug":"παρακλιδόν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n78199\" key=\"paraklido/n\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">παρα-κλῐδόν</orth>, <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">παρακλίνω</etym>) <sense id=\"n78199.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">turning aside, swerving</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐκ ἂν ἔγωγε ἄλλα παρὲξ εἴποιμι π</foreign>. would not tell you another tale beside the mark and <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">swerving from the truth</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:348\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.348</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὄσσε π. ἔτραπεν ἄλλῃ</foreign> she turned her eyes <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">aside,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">h.Ven.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">182</biblScope> </bibl> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">π. πῖπτεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:757\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.757</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n78199.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">leaning against</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τοίχων ἔνθα καὶ ἔνθα π</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0579.tlg002:559\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Orph.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a><